reviewText:
It explains everything in detail. Easy to follow!
Fun it's just great great, great! It is everything I expected and more.

Pick this DVD up when I was vacationing in Thailand.  Love this DVD.  This is the best Muay Thai instructional and history of the art in my DVD collection.  The production and the narration are excellent.  However, next to impossible to find this DVD in the U.S.  Glad I got mine!
